window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Daisy McDare's latest decorating job turns into a crime scene when Adam Dunning, the arrogant owner of a French restaurant, is found stabbed in the back. As Daisy starts digging deeper, she realizes Adam had a knack for making enemies. Between Adam's bitter wife, needy mistress, unhappy staff, and scheming daughter, Daisy has her hands full in trying to crack the case.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Daisy arms herself with cupcakes, one-liners, and plenty of spunk to find the killer before they strike again.&nbsp;</p>"; 
